node.text:
Please join us in praying for the nation of South Africa. Many are facing joblessness and a lack of food in the aftermath of a turbulent week.
•
We have partnered with KwaCare to distribute food to the most affected communities in the province of KwaZulu-Natal, bringing relief to those who have been cut off from the food supply chain and the many who have lost their jobs. Pray that God would bring His peace and comfort to all those who have been affected.
•
Thank you for helping us share Christ and love people during these difficult times!

node.text:
As Sonia limped into the clinic in El Salvador, she had no idea it would change her life forever. As a result of her diabetes, her feet had gone numb—bleeding from animal bites that she hadn’t even noticed. After her feet had been cleaned and bandaged, our team offered to pray with her, and she received Jesus as her Savior. When she came back several months later, she couldn’t keep the smile off her face!
•

node.text:
I challenge you today to believe God's Word about your life. If you have ever doubted that He has a purpose for your life, it's time to change your mind.
•
If you have ever wondered whether He has good plans for you, it's time to believe it with all your heart. I guarantee you: You have a great future ahead. All you have to do is believe it and embrace it.
•
"Lord, thank You for having such a great plan for my life. Help me to embrace it with all my heart!"
